 CITADEL: IN-GAME KEYS:
------------------------

 ARROWS,MOUSE,JOY,NUMERIC - movement
 LMB                      - forward movement
 ENTER,SHIFT,RMB          - shoot/press/examine/use
 1-8, +/-                 - screen size
 F1-F7                    - change weapon
 F8-F10                   - select magnetic card
 F                        - floors on/off
 P                        - pause
 D                        - detail level (low/medium/high)
 Z                        - disturbances on/off
 N                        